# Education Content Sync

## Activation

Activates when editing:
- backend/services/market/regime_engine.py
- backend/services/market/stage_classifier.py
- backend/services/market/scan_engine.py
- backend/services/market/quad_engine.py
- backend/services/execution/exit_cascade.py
- backend/services/execution/risk_gate.py
- frontend/src/pages/MarketEducation.tsx
- frontend/src/data/glossary.json
- frontend/src/components/education/StageChartExample.tsx
- docs/STAGE_ANALYSIS_SPEC.md

## When Editing Backend Engine Files

If you change ANY threshold, formula, classification rule, scoring boundary, or behavioral logic:
1. Check if the education files reflect this change
2. Update education content in the same PR
3. glossary.json is the single source for tooltip text — update it, not inline copies

## When Editing Education Files

1. Read the actual backend source before writing any threshold or rule
2. Never invent or assume values — verify from code
3. Cross-check MarketEducation.tsx, glossary.json, and StageChartExample.tsx for consistency
